#Accounts ---------------------------------------------------------------------
IMAPAccount gmail
AuthMechs LOGIN
Host imap.gmail.com
User michielvdnheuvel
PassCmd "pass show mail/michielvdnheuvel@gmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPAccount eforah
AuthMechs LOGIN
Host imap.gmail.com
User michiel@eforah.nl
PassCmd "pass show mail/michiel@eforah.nl"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

